      "speaker": "郭芙蓉",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "她想出家就让她去，还追她干嘛？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "吕秀才",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "你懂啥，男人除了感情还要有责任心。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "李大嘴",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "就是，人家本来好好的，就因为你，把一辈子都毁了。你不内疚吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "佟湘玉",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "就算你们说得都有道理，呆会他要说半句不合适的话，你们就都跟着倒霉。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "description": "白展堂、展红绫下楼"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "你听我说，站住，站住。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "展红绫",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "你放开我，让我走我求求你了"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "行，要走也行，先喝一杯权当是给你饯行了。七十多年的女儿红，我自己都不舍得喝。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "佟湘玉",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "speaker-action",
          "description": "悄声"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "那是我的女儿红，我的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "什么声儿？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "郭芙蓉",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "speaker-action",
          "description": "学老鼠叫"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "吱吱~"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "展红绫",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "喝完了，我可以走了吧。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "啧，着什么急呀，来再喝一杯。从我们这往北啊，十里地，有一尼姑庵，全天候营业。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "展红绫",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "他就从来不会这么跟我说话。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "白展堂",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "他是兵，我是贼，这怎么比呀。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "speaker": "展红绫",
      "performances": [
        {
          "type": "line",
          "line": "我俩头一次见面的情形，你还记得吗？"
        }
      ]
